    "causal_summary": "The entire memory surface was down at session start on 2026-07-03 and the loss was silent: a dist-freshness bootstrap deadlock that `npm run build` (exit 0) cannot clear blocked the CLI shim (live-reproduced twice, deep-dive Chain C), the stale condition was misclassified as retryable exit 75 while hooks fail open, and the daemon's context-server had been crash-looping with SIGBUS earlier that morning (launcher log 05:52-06:07)",
